                              "type": "string",
                              "description": "The type of Cloudlet that this policy is for. To see the available Cloudlets, run the [List Cloudlets](ref:get-cloudlets) operation. Possible values include: `ALB` for Application Load Balancer, `AP` for API Prioritization, `AS` for Audience Segmentation, `CD` for Phased Release, `ER` for Edge Redirector, `FR` for Forward Rewrite, `IG` for Request Control, and `VP` for Visitor Prioritization.",
